flavor_text_entries.ruby:
BANETTE generates energy for laying
strong curses by sticking pins into its
own body. This POKéMON was originally a pitiful
plush doll that was thrown away.
flavor_text_entries.sapphire:
A cursed energy permeated the stuffing
of a discarded and forgotten plush doll,
giving it new life as BANETTE. The POKéMON’s energy would escape if it
were to ever open its mouth.
flavor_text_entries.emerald:
An abandoned plush doll became this
POKéMON. They are said to live in garbage
dumps and wander about in search of the
children that threw them away.
flavor_text_entries.firered:
Strong feelings of hatred turned a puppet
into a POKéMON. If it opens its mouth,
its cursed energy escapes.

flavor_text_entries.omega-ruby:
Banette generates energy for laying strong curses by sticking
pins into its own body. This Pokémon was originally a pitiful
plush doll that was thrown away.
flavor_text_entries.alpha-sapphire:
A cursed energy permeated the stuffing of a discarded and
forgotten plush doll, giving it new life as Banette.
The Pokémon’s energy would escape if it were to ever open
its mouth.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-sun:
It’s a stuffed toy that was thrown away and
became possessed, ever searching for the one
who threw it away so it can exact its revenge.
flavor_text_entries.ultra-moon:
Resentment at being cast off made it spring into
being. Some say that treating it well will satisfy
it, and it will once more become a stuffed toy.
